## Frontend

NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://cafeteria-inteligente-frontend-production.up.railway.app/

## 🐳 Execução com Docker (opcional)

docker compose up --build

## 💻 Execução local

Backend
cd backend
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
Frontend
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev

